  "title": "chore(typescript): setup Rollup and Babel builds (part 4)",
  "body": "This is the fourth step toward our process migrating to TypeScript.\r\n\r\n- **Rollup**.\r\n  - Allow the UMD build to accept many extensions, including `ts` and `tsx` (others are for imported modules).\r\n- **CJS and ES**.\r\n  - Allow Babel to compile `ts` and `tsx` files.\r\n  - Update pattern matching for test and mock files to be correctly ignored with Babel 7.\r\n- **Types**.\r\n  - Add React and Lodash types for migrating our codebase later.\r\n\r\n### Related\r\n\r\n- Part 1: #3411\r\n- Part 2: #3412\r\n- Part 3: #3413\r\n- Part 5: #3417",
